 n\pars{n + 1}\ldots\pars{n + r - 1}={\pars{n + r -1}! \over \pars{n - 1}!} ={\pars{n + r -1}! \over \pars{n - 1}!r!}\,r! = {n + r - 1 \choose r}r! 
 {n\pars{n + 1}\ldots\pars{n + r - 1} \over r!} = {n + r - 1 \choose r} \quad\mbox{which is an integer !!!}  
